# Implement workflow (Gurotopia)

When implementing protocol features from official captures:

1. Follow `c:\VS_Repos\captures\agents\IMPLEMENT.md` and `AGENTS.md` in this repo.
2. Only implement folders with STATUS `ready` (or as named by the user).
3. Do not invent packets — if the brief is incomplete, set STATUS `blocked` and request a re-capture.
4. Register every new handler in the correct pool (`__action.cpp`, `__dialog_return.cpp`, `__states.cpp`).
5. Verify via GTProxy `run/config.gurotopia.json`, then update the feature `notes.md` and `captures/TODO.md`.
